A simple health-related service or activity delivered by a clinician, organisation or agency.

author.name: Silje Ljosland Bakke, John Tore Valand, Terje Sagmyr
Ana Paula Pannuti, Débora Farage, Adriana Kitajima, Fernanda Maia e Clóvis Puttini.

at0000.1.description: Request for a health-related service or activity to be delivered by a clinician, organisation or agency.

at0121.1.description: The name of the single service or activity requested.
at0121.1.comment: Coding of the 'Service name' with a coding system is desirable, if available. For example: 'referral' to an endocrinologist for diabetes management.

at0010.1.description: The local identifier assigned by the requesting clinical system.
at0010.1.comment: Usually equivalent to the HL7 Placer Order Identifier.

author.name: Silje Ljosland Bakke, Marit Alice Venheim
author.organisation: Nasjonal IKT HF, Norway, Helse Vest IKT

author.name: Francesca Frexia
author.organisation: CRS4 - Center for advanced studies, research and development in Sardinia, Pula (Cagliari), Italy

at0009.1.description: The period of time before or after the named event when the activity should take place. Negative durations can be used to signify that the activity should be taken before a known event.
at0009.1.comment: For example: '3 days after onset of menstruation = menstrual onset + 3 days', '2 weeks prior to admission= admission -2 weeks'.

at0001.1.description: The activity should take place on a specific date or a specific range of dates.
at0001.1.comment: For example: 'on 12 Jan 2017' or 'on 30 Oct 2017 to 6 Nov 2017'.

at0006.1.description: The activity should take place in relation to a specific named event.

at0001.2.description: The activity should take place on a specific date or a specific range of dates.
at0001.2.comment: For example: 'on 12 Jan 2017' or 'on 30 Oct 2017 to 6 Nov 2017'.

at0001.2.description: A atividade deve ocorrer em uma data específica.
Aktiviteten skal utføres på en spesifikk dato eller i henhold til et spesifikt datointervall.
at0001.2.comment: For eksempel "12. jan 2017" eller "30 okt 2017 til 6 nov 2017".

at0001.2.description: Die Aktivität sollte an einem bestimmten Datum oder in einem bestimmten Datumsbereich stattfinden.
at0001.2.comment: Zum Beispiel: "am 12. Januar 2017" oder "vom 30. Oktober 2017 bis 6. November 2017"

author.name: Silje Ljosland Bakke
author.organisation: Nasjonal IKT HF, Helse Vest IKT AS

at0000.1.description: An entity comprising one or more people and having a particular purpose.
at0000.1.comment: For example: a company, institution, association, network, department, community group, healthcare practice group, payer/insurer, care team, or a group of neighbours who provide care or support.

at0004.1.description: The relationship or role of the organisation to the individual or subject of care.
at0004.1.comment: For example: oncologist; palliative care home nursing service; or informal support network.

at0001.1.description: The unstructured name or label for the organisation.
at0001.1.comment: For example: 'Royal Children's Hospital'; 'ABC District Nursing Service'; 'YNWA Oslo' or 'JB Smith Lawyers'.
